Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.02,0:17:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾即为汝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.71,0:17:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝即为吾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.76,0:17:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝是为开启门扉之人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.60,0:18:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才是怎么一回事啊
